spec_data.Name: clutter-gst2-devel
spec_data.Description:
Clutter is an open source software library for creating fast, visually
rich and animated graphical user interfaces.

Clutter GStreamer enables the use of GStreamer with Clutter.

The clutter-gst2-devel package contains libraries and header files for
developing applications that use clutter-gst API version 2.0.
